00:56:24,020 --> 00:56:25,630
Rebecca?

584
00:56:26,530 --> 00:56:27,930
Hả?

585
00:56:29,360 --> 00:56:31,830
Chị thấy thuốc chưa?

586
00:56:33,900 --> 00:56:35,390
Chưa.

587
00:56:36,250 --> 00:56:38,560
Nhưng rồi mình sẽ nghĩ cách sau.

588
00:56:38,920 --> 00:56:40,880
Chị nghĩ thế à?

589
00:56:43,050 --> 00:56:44,710
Ừ.

590
00:56:45,840 --> 00:56:48,230
Chúng ta phải chữa bệnh cho mẹ.

591
00:56:49,330 --> 00:56:51,040
Vâng.

592
00:56:52,000 --> 00:56:54,000
Ngủ đi em.

593
00:57:15,480 --> 00:57:16,960
Mẹ kiếp!

594
00:57:32,880 --> 00:57:34,360
Bret?

595
00:57:39,260 --> 00:57:40,750
Bret?

596
00:57:52,510 --> 00:57:54,170
Mẹ nó.

597
00:58:32,310 --> 00:58:33,790
Mẹ nó.

598
00:58:41,620 --> 00:58:43,260
Thôi nào.

599
00:58:47,280 --> 00:58:48,950
Rebecca!

600
00:58:58,660 --> 00:59:00,180
Rebecca?

601
00:59:06,610 --> 00:59:08,170
Rebecca?

602
00:59:26,140 --> 00:59:27,770
Rebecca?

603
00:59:33,920 --> 00:59:35,470
Becca.

604
00:59:58,980 --> 01:00:01,720
Không!

605
01:00:18,630 --> 01:00:20,190
Thôi nào.

606
01:00:21,400 --> 01:00:23,450
- Chị làm gì thế?
- Em làm gì vậy?

607
01:00:23,500 --> 01:00:25,260
Đừng bỏ em đi chứ.

608
01:00:25,280 --> 01:00:27,520
- Ừ.
- Đừng bao giờ!

609
01:00:27,540 --> 01:00:29,660
Ừ, được rồi.

610
01:00:30,770 --> 01:00:32,330
Hỏng rồi.

611
01:00:32,360 --> 01:00:34,420
Còn gì nữa à?

612
01:00:36,640 --> 01:00:38,190
Mắc lừa rồi.

613
01:00:40,150 --> 01:00:41,600
Không.

614
01:00:42,180 --> 01:00:44,870
Không!

615
01:00:44,870 --> 01:00:46,250
Cứu với!

616
01:00:46,270 --> 01:00:48,090
- Cứu với!
- Bret!

617
01:00:48,110 --> 01:00:50,360
Thả bọn tôi ra!

618
